snippet.textDisplay:
When I first listen to this song I wasn't in such mood therefore the song didn't hit that much to me. After I listen it some times later I realized that to judge or react on a song you should need to be in the mood according to the song so that you could emotionally connect with that feeling it's very important for the listeners so that they understand the singer's expressions of vocals.
Although a wonderful effort by Abdul hanan and ofcourse the Jafar part has no match to anything he's pure a different soul.
